<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="16Jul1936"><font color="red">16 July 1936</font> <i>NLPK</i> (from Paul L&eacute;on to J. Ralph Pinker): I am in correspondence with &hellip; Messrs John Lane about queries which I am answering direct as I do not think it worth while to bother you. </div>
